                        <h3 class="quarter-top-margin">Who We Are.</h3>
                        <p>We're a community of aircraft maintenance engineers, designers, industry experts, pilots and enthusiasts who have had years of experience in the aviation and aircraft industry. Our community members hold high ranks in India'a biggest airlines, airforce and international airlines.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-block">
                        <h3 class="quarter-top-margin">Our Mission.</h3>
                        <p>We aim to provide quality and educational resources to Indian students to double the number of aircraft maintenance engineers and pilots passing from various Indian institutuions every year.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-block">
                        <h3 class="quarter-top-margin">Our Vision.</h3>
                        <p>We can clearly see the future scope of aviation and aircraft engineering and we dream Indian engineers and pilots to play significant role in global industry future.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-block">
                        <h3 class="quarter-top-margin">Our Values.</h3>
                        <p>Our aim is to educate Indians and motivate them to not only join AME and other aviation courses but to consider this domain as a significant one for the growth of our nation. We can leave a footprint of achievements on the globe with the help of young minds. This is what we believe in.</p>
